      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! Here is a fantastic opportunity to get your hands on a vehicle with tons of potential. While it's currently in rough shape and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic work to get back to its best, it serves as a wonderful blank canvas for a restoration project or a valuable source of parts. If you love bringing a classic back to life, this is the one for you!",
