      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily transportation. While it is mechanically sound and drives well, potential buyers should expect some visible wear, including minor dents, scratches on the exterior, and some staining on the interior upholstery. It has higher mileage, but it has been regularly maintained and is ready for its next owner.",
