    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently has difficulty starting and runs roughly, suggesting it may need a major overhaul or replacement soon. There are visible signs of heavy wear throughout, including several rust spots on the exterior panels and significant staining and tears in the interior upholstery. The transmission also exhibits slipping during gear changes. This car is best suited as a parts donor or a dedicated project for someone with the tools and time for a full restoration.",
